# Exetasi Project Overview

Quiz and exam webapp (monorepo). Full spec in `Requirements.md`.

## Stack
- Frontend: **Quasar 2** (Vue 3 / TypeScript) in `frontend/`, hash-mode SPA + Capacitor mobile
- Backend: **FastAPI** (Python) in `backend/`, REST API
- Database: **PostgreSQL** (root `docker-compose.yml`; `make db-up` from repo root)
- State: **Pinia** | Routing: **Vue Router 4** | i18n: **vue-i18n 11**

## Commands
Repository root / `frontend/` as appropriate:

```bash
make db-up                              # Postgres via docker compose (default)
make db-up COMPOSE='nerdctl compose'    # same via containerd + nerdctl

pnpm dev      # dev server (workspace → frontend)
pnpm build    # production build
pnpm lint     # ESLint
pnpm format   # Prettier
```

## Non-Negotiable Conventions
- **pnpm only** — never suggest npm or yarn commands
- **`<script setup lang="ts">`** in every SFC — no Options API
- **All UI strings through `t('key')`** — no hardcoded copy anywhere
- **Strict TypeScript** — no `any`, no unsafe `as` casts
- **Quasar components** (`QBtn`, `QInput`, `QCard`…) over native HTML equivalents
